foot_85
(126-5) Q: How to remove spiritual sloth of others?
A: Have you removed your own? Turn your enquiries towards Self search. The force set up within you will operate on others also.
(126-6) Q: What about PB's idea of inspired action?
A: Let activities go on. They do not affect the pure Self.

